67
00:04:56,898 --> 00:04:59,107
Please,
it's always Frank to you.

68
00:04:59,108 --> 00:05:02,318
I came because you asked me,
but don't mistake that for false hope.

69
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:04,195
If you have other people
to lobby, you should.

70
00:05:04,196 --> 00:05:06,487
- Ten minutes.
- It won't change anything.

71
00:05:06,488 --> 00:05:08,907
Well, at the very least,
enjoy the free coffee.

72
00:05:08,908 --> 00:05:11,075
- I don't drink caffeine.
- Then decaf.

73
00:05:11,076 --> 00:05:13,911
- Still has caffeine.
- Well, enjoy the free oxygen.

74
00:05:13,912 --> 00:05:16,162
It gets stuffy over there
in the Longworth building.

75
00:05:16,163 --> 00:05:18,915
- Coffee for me, and...
- Seltzer water, if you have it.

76
00:05:18,916 --> 00:05:20,875
I'm sure we do.

77
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:29,464
Now, I can understand
if you might hold a grudge.

78
00:05:29,465 --> 00:05:32,007
I don't hold grudges, Frank.
I just don't negotiate

79
00:05:32,008 --> 00:05:34,343
with people who are
fundamentally deceptive.

80
00:05:34,344 --> 00:05:36,010
I never lied to you, Donald.

81
00:05:36,011 --> 00:05:38,679
You promised to seek my counsel,
which you never once did.

82
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:42,724
